      <title>马乔里·泰勒·格林威胁解除约翰逊众议院议长职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/republican-greene-threatens-to-remove-johnson-as-house-speaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党众议员马乔里·泰勒·格林 (Marjorie Taylor Greene) 周五迈出了第一步，罢免了迈克·约翰逊 (Mike Johnson) 众议院议长职务，并威胁称，共和党可能会在 11 月大选前再次进行改组，并引发更多内讧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/republican-greene-threatens-to-remove-johnson-as-house-speaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 16:06:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院在关闭截止日期前几小时通过了 1.2 万亿美元法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/house-passes-1-2-trillion-bill-hours-before-shutdown-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院在周五午夜部分政府关闭最后期限前几小时通过了一项 1.2 万亿美元的政府拨款法案，拒绝了共和党强硬派大幅削减国内支出的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/house-passes-1-2-trillion-bill-hours-before-shutdown-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 15:46:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称债券截止日期前他拥有“近 5 亿美元”现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/trump-says-he-has-almost-500-million-cash-amid-bond-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，他手头有近 5 亿美元现金，这笔巨额资金仍不足以支付这位前总统在纽约州民事欺诈诉讼中三天后到期的上诉保证金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/trump-says-he-has-almost-500-million-cash-amid-bond-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 15:12:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大政府支出增长速度是收入增长速度的两倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/canada-government-spending-grows-at-twice-the-pace-of-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着财政部长克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰准备下个月提交预算，加拿大政府支出的增长速度快于收入的增长速度，利息支付持续攀升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/canada-government-spending-grows-at-twice-the-pace-of-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 15:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔前总统瓦德的政党在三月投票中支持费耶</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/senegal-ex-president-wade-s-party-backs-faye-in-march-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔前总统阿卜杜拉耶·瓦德 (Abdoulaye Wade) 领导的塞内加尔民主党在 3 月 24 日总统选举之前表示支持反对派候选人巴西鲁·迪奥马耶·法耶 (Bassirou Diomaye Faye)，这可能会改变游戏规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/senegal-ex-president-wade-s-party-backs-faye-in-march-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 14:42:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
